      "role": "user",
      "content": "i don't even know why i'm talking to you. it just feels like i've hit a wall. like, i've spent so many years trying to heal and fix myself and everything that happened to me, but it's just... it's not working. i feel like there's nothing left to even try with. i think i'm just fundamentally broken.",
