    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels like no matter what i do, the core of me is just... damaged. like a machine that's been crushed too many times. you say it's okay to stop trying to fix it, but doesn't that just mean accepting that i'll always be this way? that i'm just a lost cause?",
